OL,3,CTougher rules proposed to improve
OL,4,Canimal welfare in Guernsey
OL,6,FImprovements to animal welfare law
OL,7,Fhave been proposed.
OL,9,FThe legislation would give greater
OL,10,Fenforcement powers to investigators
OL,11,Fand also bring the island in line with
OL,12,Fthe UK Animal Welfare Act 2024.
OL,14,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez says the
OL,15,Fchanges would protect Guernsey's
OL,16,Fdomestic animals, resident wildlife
OL,17,Fand migratory species.
