OL,3,CTougher rules proposed to improve
OL,4,Canimal welfare in Guernsey
OL,6,FThe proposition has been prompted by
OL,7,Freports that British livestock
OL,8,Ftransported across the EU suffer from
OL,9,Fthirst, exhaustion and rough handling.
OL,11,FThe law would restrict exporting
OL,12,Flivestock for the 'slaughter or
OL,13,Ffattening for slaughter' beyond the
OL,14,FBritish Isles.
OL,16,FOther changes include:
