OL,3,CTougher rules proposed to improve
OL,4,Canimal welfare in Guernsey
OL,6,FThe proposals would also bring
OL,7,FGuernsey legislation in line with
OL,8,FEngland, Scotland and Wales by
OL,9,Fprohibiting or restricting the use of
OL,10,F'indiscriminate traps'.
OL,12,F'Indiscriminate' devices entrap or
OL,13,Fkill animals but can also affect
OL,14,Fspecies that are not the intended
OL,15,Ftarget.
OL,17,FStates Veterinary Officer David
OL,18,FChamberlain explains: "Snares, leg-
OL,19,Fhold/gin traps and glue traps are
OL,20,Fcruel by design and can cause enormous
OL,21,Fanimal suffering.
